# Space Invaders game example # {#HERO_BOARD_GAME_INVADERS}
  
This example draws the classic space invaders game screen and allows the ship to
be moved left and right. It is not meant to be a full game. The LCD's refresh
rate is way too slow and it is very noticable when the ship is moving.

File(s):
- boards/arm/stm32/px_hero/games/invaders/src/main.c

The following modules are used:
- @ref BOARDS_STM32_PX_HERO
- @ref STM32_SPI
- @ref PX_LCD_ST7567_JHD12864
- @ref PX_GFX
